{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":916,"text":"When I was preparing for this talk,"},{"time":3170,"text":"I went to search for a couple of quotes"},{"time":5146,"text":"that I can share with you."},{"time":6991,"text":"Good news: I found three"},{"time":9162,"text":"that I particularly liked,"},{"time":10994,"text":"the first by Samuel Johnson, who said,"},{"time":14472,"text":"\"When making your choice in life,"},{"time":16712,"text":"do not forget to live,\""},{"time":19468,"text":"the second by Aeschylus, who reminded us that"},{"time":23000,"text":"\"happiness is a choice that requires effort,\""},{"time":27305,"text":"and the third is one by Groucho Marx"},{"time":30830,"text":"who said, \"I wouldn't want to choose to belong"},{"time":33920,"text":"to any club that would have me as a member.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":39252,"text":"Now, bad news:"},{"time":41318,"text":"I didn't know which one of these quotes"},{"time":43429,"text":"to choose and share with you."},{"time":46178,"text":"The sweet anxiety of choice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49403,"text":"In today's times of post-industrial capitalism,"},{"time":53446,"text":"choice, together with individual freedom"},{"time":57109,"text":"and the idea of self-making,"},{"time":59970,"text":"has been elevated to an ideal."},{"time":63500,"text":"Now, together with this, we also have a belief"},{"time":67387,"text":"in endless progress."},{"time":70155,"text":"But the underside of this ideology"},{"time":72911,"text":"has been an increase of anxiety,"},{"time":76443,"text":"feelings of guilt,"},{"time":78513,"text":"feelings of being inadequate,"},{"time":82217,"text":"feeling that we are failing in our choices."},{"time":86954,"text":"Sadly, this ideology of individual choice"},{"time":90950,"text":"has prevented us from thinking about social changes."},{"time":96400,"text":"It appears that this ideology was actually"},{"time":99319,"text":"very efficient in pacifying us"},{"time":102001,"text":"as political and social thinkers."},{"time":104797,"text":"Instead of making social critiques,"},{"time":107113,"text":"we are more and more engaging in self-critique,"},{"time":110869,"text":"sometimes to the point of self-destruction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115122,"text":"Now, how come that ideology of choice"},{"time":117867,"text":"is still so powerful,"},{"time":119450,"text":"even among people who have"},{"time":122546,"text":"not many things to choose among?"},{"time":124655,"text":"How come that even people who are poor"},{"time":128229,"text":"very much still identify with the idea of choice,"},{"time":132620,"text":"the kind of rational idea of choice"},{"time":134689,"text":"which we embrace?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":137322,"text":"Now, the ideology of choice is very successful"},{"time":141340,"text":"in opening for us a space to think"},{"time":145320,"text":"about some imagined future."},{"time":148987,"text":"Let me give you an example."},{"time":151000,"text":"My friend Manya,"},{"time":152913,"text":"when she was a student at university in California,"},{"time":155962,"text":"was earning money"},{"time":157660,"text":"by working for a car dealer."},{"time":160720,"text":"Now, Manya, when she encountered"},{"time":162531,"text":"the typical customer, would debate with him"},{"time":165389,"text":"about his lifestyle,"},{"time":167233,"text":"how much he wants to spend,"},{"time":169956,"text":"how many children he has,"},{"time":171700,"text":"what does he need the car for?"},{"time":173973,"text":"They would usually come to a good conclusion"},{"time":176660,"text":"what would be a perfect car."},{"time":179214,"text":"Now, before Manya's customer would go home"},{"time":182702,"text":"and think things through,"},{"time":185140,"text":"she would say to him,"},{"time":186960,"text":"\"The car that you are buying now is perfect,"},{"time":190745,"text":"but in a few year's time,"},{"time":192770,"text":"when your kids will be already out of the house,"},{"time":195403,"text":"when you will have a little bit more money,"},{"time":198370,"text":"that other car will be ideal."},{"time":201399,"text":"But what you are buying now is great.\""},{"time":204936,"text":"Now, the majority of Manya's customers"},{"time":207293,"text":"who came back the next day"},{"time":208913,"text":"bought that other car,"},{"time":211738,"text":"the car they did not need,"},{"time":213795,"text":"the car that cost far too much money."},{"time":216833,"text":"Now, Manya became so successful in selling cars"},{"time":219769,"text":"that soon she moved on to selling airplanes."},{"time":222671,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":227265,"text":"And knowing so much about\nthe psychology of people"},{"time":231350,"text":"prepared her well for her current job,"},{"time":232924,"text":"which is that of a psychoanalyst."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236755,"text":"Now, why were Manya's customers so irrational?"},{"time":241278,"text":"Manya's success was that she was able"},{"time":243775,"text":"to open in their heads an image"},{"time":246700,"text":"of an idealized future,"},{"time":250280,"text":"an image of themselves"},{"time":252190,"text":"when they are already more successful, freer,"},{"time":256420,"text":"and for them, choosing that other car"},{"time":258669,"text":"was as if they are coming closer to this ideal"},{"time":261729,"text":"in which it was as if Manya already saw them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266578,"text":"Now, we rarely make really totally rational choices."},{"time":270981,"text":"Choices are influenced by our unconscious,"},{"time":274559,"text":"by our community."},{"time":276398,"text":"We're often choosing"},{"time":278328,"text":"by guessing, what would other people"},{"time":280482,"text":"think about our choice?"},{"time":283466,"text":"Also we are choosing"},{"time":284671,"text":"by looking at what others are choosing."},{"time":287040,"text":"We're also guessing what is\nsocially acceptable choice."},{"time":291845,"text":"Now, because of this, we actually"},{"time":294916,"text":"even after we have already chosen,"},{"time":296805,"text":"like bought a car,"},{"time":298560,"text":"endlessly read reviews about cars,"},{"time":301710,"text":"as if we still want to convince ourselves"},{"time":304070,"text":"that we made the right choice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306671,"text":"Now, choices are anxiety-provoking."},{"time":309870,"text":"They are linked to risks, losses."},{"time":312951,"text":"They are highly unpredictable."},{"time":315306,"text":"Now, because of this,"},{"time":317415,"text":"people have now more and more problems"},{"time":319918,"text":"that they are not choosing anything."},{"time":323376,"text":"Not long ago, I was at a wedding reception,"},{"time":327207,"text":"and I met a young, beautiful woman"},{"time":329511,"text":"who immediately started telling\nme about her anxiety over choice."},{"time":334137,"text":"She said to me, \"I needed one month"},{"time":336108,"text":"to decide which dress to wear.\""},{"time":339154,"text":"Then she said, \"For weeks I was researching"},{"time":341675,"text":"which hotel to stay for this one night."},{"time":344936,"text":"And now, I need to choose a sperm donor.\""},{"time":349434,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":352201,"text":"I looked at this woman in shock."},{"time":355700,"text":"\"Sperm donor? What's the rush?\""},{"time":358737,"text":"She said, \"I'm turning 40 at the end of this year,"},{"time":362911,"text":"and I've been so bad in choosing men in my life.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":367736,"text":"Now choice, because it's linked to risk,"},{"time":372142,"text":"is anxiety-provoking,"},{"time":374419,"text":"and it was already the famous"},{"time":377276,"text":"Danish philosopher Søren Kierkegaard"},{"time":379869,"text":"who pointed out that anxiety"},{"time":382583,"text":"is linked to the possibility of possibility."},{"time":385848,"text":"Now, we think today that we can prevent these risks."},{"time":390281,"text":"We have endless market analysis,"},{"time":393362,"text":"projections of the future earnings."},{"time":395871,"text":"Even with market, which is about chance,"},{"time":398571,"text":"randomness, we think we can predict rationally"},{"time":402711,"text":"where it's going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404434,"text":"Now, chance is actually becoming very traumatic."},{"time":409281,"text":"Last year, my friend Bernard Harcourt"},{"time":412171,"text":"at the University of Chicago organized an event,"},{"time":416446,"text":"a conference on the idea of chance."},{"time":419843,"text":"He and I were together on the panel,"},{"time":421929,"text":"and just before delivering our papers —"},{"time":424446,"text":"we didn't know each other's papers —"},{"time":426796,"text":"we decided to take chance seriously."},{"time":429304,"text":"So we informed our audience"},{"time":431140,"text":"that what they will just now hear"},{"time":433489,"text":"will be a random paper,"},{"time":435502,"text":"a mixture of the two papers"},{"time":437674,"text":"which we didn't know what each was writing."},{"time":441545,"text":"Now, we delivered the conference in such a way."},{"time":445725,"text":"Bernard read his first paragraph,"},{"time":447946,"text":"I read my first paragraph,"},{"time":450070,"text":"Bernard read his second paragraph,"},{"time":452277,"text":"I read my second paragraph,"},{"time":453762,"text":"in this way towards the end of our papers."},{"time":457384,"text":"Now, you will be surprised"},{"time":459263,"text":"that a majority of our audience"},{"time":461445,"text":"did not think that what they'd just listened to"},{"time":464188,"text":"was a completely random paper."},{"time":467473,"text":"They couldn't believe that"},{"time":469419,"text":"speaking from the position of authority"},{"time":471939,"text":"like two professors we were,"},{"time":473817,"text":"we would take chance seriously."},{"time":476888,"text":"They thought we prepared the papers together"},{"time":479475,"text":"and were just joking that it's random."}]},{"cues":[{"time":482953,"text":"Now, we live in times with a lot of information,"},{"time":487120,"text":"big data,"},{"time":488711,"text":"a lot of knowledge about the insides of our bodies."},{"time":491715,"text":"We decoded our genome."},{"time":493458,"text":"We know about our brains more than before."},{"time":496569,"text":"But surprisingly, people are more and more"},{"time":499205,"text":"turning a blind eye in front of this knowledge."},{"time":503640,"text":"Ignorance and denial are on the rise."},{"time":508633,"text":"Now, in regard to the current economic crisis,"},{"time":511851,"text":"we think that we will just wake up again"},{"time":514505,"text":"and everything will be the same as before,"},{"time":516721,"text":"and no political or social changes are needed."},{"time":519984,"text":"In regard to ecological crisis,"},{"time":522234,"text":"we think nothing needs to be done just now,"},{"time":525350,"text":"or others need to act before us."},{"time":528252,"text":"Or even when ecological crisis already happens,"},{"time":531548,"text":"like a catastrophe in Fukushima,"},{"time":533877,"text":"often we have people living in the same environment"},{"time":536701,"text":"with the same amount of information,"},{"time":538523,"text":"and half of them will be anxious about radiation"},{"time":542210,"text":"and half of them will ignore it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545531,"text":"Now, psychoanalysts know very well"},{"time":548343,"text":"that people surprisingly don't have"},{"time":550818,"text":"passion for knowledge"},{"time":552607,"text":"but passion for ignorance."},{"time":555689,"text":"Now, what does that mean?"},{"time":557174,"text":"Let's say when we are facing"},{"time":558990,"text":"a life-threatening illness,"},{"time":561783,"text":"a lot of people don't want to know that."},{"time":564989,"text":"They'd rather prefer denying the illness,"},{"time":568387,"text":"which is why it's not so wise to inform them"},{"time":571661,"text":"if they don't ask."},{"time":573370,"text":"Surprisingly, research shows that sometimes"},{"time":575800,"text":"people who deny their illness"},{"time":577644,"text":"live longer than those who are rationally choosing"},{"time":581560,"text":"the best treatment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583999,"text":"Now, this ignorance, however,"},{"time":586120,"text":"is not very helpful on the level of the social."},{"time":590849,"text":"When we are ignorant about where we are heading,"},{"time":594179,"text":"a lot of social damage can be caused."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598364,"text":"Now, on top of facing ignorance,"},{"time":600445,"text":"we are also facing today"},{"time":602683,"text":"some kind of an obviousness."},{"time":605844,"text":"Now, it was French philosopher"},{"time":607971,"text":"Louis Althusser who pointed out"},{"time":610080,"text":"that ideology functions in such a way"},{"time":612643,"text":"that it creates a veil of obviousness."},{"time":616509,"text":"Before we do any social critique,"},{"time":620244,"text":"it is necessary really to lift that veil of obviousness"},{"time":624631,"text":"and to think through a little bit differently."},{"time":627960,"text":"If we go back to this ideology"},{"time":629997,"text":"of individual, rational choice"},{"time":632528,"text":"we often embrace,"},{"time":634856,"text":"it's necessary precisely here"},{"time":636836,"text":"to lift this obviousness"},{"time":639165,"text":"and to think a little bit differently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":642296,"text":"Now for me, a question often is"},{"time":645260,"text":"why we still embrace this idea of a self-made man"},{"time":649863,"text":"on which capitalism relied from its beginning?"},{"time":653395,"text":"Why do we think that we are really such masters"},{"time":655880,"text":"of our lives that we can rationally"},{"time":658705,"text":"make the best ideal choices,"},{"time":661157,"text":"that we don't accept losses and risks?"},{"time":664386,"text":"And for me, it's very shocking to\nsee sometimes very poor people,"},{"time":667671,"text":"for example, not supporting the idea"},{"time":670015,"text":"of the rich being taxed more."},{"time":673633,"text":"Quite often here they still identify"},{"time":675681,"text":"with a certain kind of a lottery mentality."},{"time":678279,"text":"Okay, maybe they don't think that they will make it"},{"time":681562,"text":"in the future, but maybe they think,"},{"time":682964,"text":"my son might become the next Bill Gates."},{"time":686153,"text":"And who would want to tax one's son?"},{"time":689370,"text":"Or, a question for me is also,"},{"time":693200,"text":"why would people who have no health insurance"},{"time":695580,"text":"not embrace universal healthcare?"},{"time":698561,"text":"Sometimes they don't embrace it,"},{"time":700090,"text":"again identifying with the idea of choice,"},{"time":702914,"text":"but they have nothing to choose from."}]},{"cues":[{"time":705472,"text":"Now, Margaret Thatcher famously said"},{"time":709922,"text":"that there is nothing like a society."},{"time":712554,"text":"Society doesn't exist, it is only individuals"},{"time":716334,"text":"and their families."},{"time":718130,"text":"Sadly, this ideology still functions very well,"},{"time":723263,"text":"which is why people who are poor might feel"},{"time":725547,"text":"ashamed for their poverty."},{"time":727470,"text":"We might endlessly feel guilty that we are"},{"time":729732,"text":"not making the right choices,"},{"time":731846,"text":"and that's why we didn't succeed."},{"time":734142,"text":"We are anxious that we are not good enough."},{"time":737674,"text":"That's why we work very hard,"},{"time":739597,"text":"long hours at the workplace"},{"time":741138,"text":"and equally long hours on remaking ourselves."},{"time":745576,"text":"Now, when we are anxious over choices,"},{"time":747989,"text":"sometimes we easily give our power of choice away."},{"time":752421,"text":"We identify with the guru"},{"time":754217,"text":"who tells us what to do,"},{"time":755496,"text":"self-help therapist,"},{"time":758140,"text":"or we embrace a totalitarian leader"},{"time":760919,"text":"who appears to have no doubts about choices,"},{"time":763706,"text":"who sort of knows."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765790,"text":"Now, often people ask me,"},{"time":768566,"text":"\"What did you learn by studying choice?\""},{"time":770940,"text":"And there is an important message that I did learn."},{"time":774111,"text":"When thinking about choices,"},{"time":776598,"text":"I stopped taking choices too seriously, personally."},{"time":781558,"text":"First, I realized a lot of choice I make"},{"time":784180,"text":"is not rational."},{"time":785639,"text":"It's linked to my unconscious,"},{"time":787543,"text":"my guesses of what others are choosing,"},{"time":789737,"text":"or what is a socially embraced choice."},{"time":793393,"text":"I also embrace the idea"},{"time":795690,"text":"that we should go beyond"},{"time":797330,"text":"thinking about individual choices,"},{"time":799254,"text":"that it's very important to rethink social choices,"},{"time":802910,"text":"since this ideology of individual\nchoice has pacified us."},{"time":806611,"text":"It really prevented us to think about social change."},{"time":809749,"text":"We spend so much time\nchoosing things for ourselves"},{"time":813480,"text":"and barely reflect on"},{"time":815250,"text":"communal choices we can make."}]},{"cues":[{"time":817476,"text":"Now, we should not forget that choice"},{"time":819176,"text":"is always linked to change."},{"time":821860,"text":"We can make individual changes,"},{"time":823676,"text":"but we can make social changes."},{"time":825861,"text":"We can choose to have more wolves."},{"time":829627,"text":"We can choose to change our environment"},{"time":832394,"text":"to have more bees."},{"time":834824,"text":"We can choose to have different rating agencies."},{"time":839110,"text":"We can choose to control corporations"},{"time":841573,"text":"instead of allowing corporations to control us."},{"time":845437,"text":"We have a possibility to make changes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":848852,"text":"Now, I started with a quote from Samuel Johnson,"},{"time":852130,"text":"who said that when we make choice in life,"},{"time":854859,"text":"we shouldn't forget to live."},{"time":857446,"text":"Finally, you can see"},{"time":859673,"text":"I did have a choice"},{"time":861180,"text":"to choose one of the three quotes"},{"time":862467,"text":"with which I wanted to start my lecture."},{"time":866491,"text":"I did have a choice,"},{"time":868390,"text":"such as nations, as people,"},{"time":870698,"text":"we have choices too to rethink"},{"time":872970,"text":"in what kind of society we want to live in the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":876282,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":878333,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}